        <div style="background: #eee; padding: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11px; border-bottom: 1px solid black; margin-top: 10px;">02. AVALIAÇÃO DE SINAIS VITAIS</div>
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 5px; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;">
            <tr>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px;"><b>P.A (mmHg)</b></td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px;"><b>TEMP (°C)</b></td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px;"><b>FC (bpm)</b></td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px;"><b>SpO2 (%)</b></td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px;"><b>GLIC (mg/dL)</b></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px;" id="pr-pa">--</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px;" id="pr-temp">--</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px;" id="pr-fc">--</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px;" id="pr-spo2">--</td>
                <td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px;" id="pr-glic">--</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div style="background: #eee; padding: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11px; border-bottom: 1px solid black; margin-top: 10px;">03. QUEIXA PRINCIPAL / AVALIAÇÃO DA ENFERMAGEM</div>
        <div style="border: 1px solid black; min-height: 80px; padding: 10px; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;" id="pr-queixa">--</div>

        <div style="margin-top: 20px; display: flex; align-items: stretch; gap: 15px;">
            <div style="border: 5px solid black; padding: 15px; flex: 1; text-align: center;">
                <p style="font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px;">PROTOCOLO DE MANCHESTER</p>
                <h2 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0;" id="pr-risco">--</h2>
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 1.5; border: 1px solid black; padding: 10px; position: relative;">
                <p style="font-size: 9px; position: absolute; bottom: 5px; right: 10px;">ASSINATURA/CARIMBO PROFISSIONAL</p>
                <div style="border-bottom: 1px dashed black; margin-top: 40px; width: 90%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 8px; color: #555;">
            SISTEMA JR HOSPITALAR - DESENVOLVIDO POR BACK INFORMATICA // VIGIA-PA
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
